data.description: Beautiful 5 bed, 2.5 bath home with almost 3,500 sqft in the highly desirable Legacy Park neighborhood, just minutes from Hwy 521 and central to all things Indian Land. The main floor has an open concept with a spacious eat-in kitchen. There’s also a separate dining room and 2 flex spaces that can be used as a home office, spare bedroom, sitting or playroom area. All bedrooms and laundry are upstairs along with a huge bonus room, perfect for a home theater or anything you can imagine. The fenced-in backyard includes a storage shed, 2 gazebos and a large deck to create the perfect outdoor sanctuary. Come check it out today!
